  <brief_title>A Study of Oral Suberoylanilide Hydroxamic Acid (SAHA) in Patients With Solid Tumors (0683-029)(COMPLETED)</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase I Clinical Study of MK0683 in Patients With Solid Tumors.</official_title>
