  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The primary purpose of this trial is to determine the maximum tolerated dose (MTD), or the
      maximum acceptable dose (MAD) and evaluate the dose limiting toxicity (DLT) of oral
      suberoylanilide hydroxamic acid in patients with solid tumors.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
